                     <interp inst="t18301028-147-person1267" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming along Piccadilly, and the officer charged me, in the King's name, to take Steed, which I did - these four pots were found on Thomas, and this strap on Steed.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301028-147-person1268">
                  HENRY 
                  HARRIS
               <interp inst="t18301028-147-person1268" type="surname" value="HARRIS"></interp>
