                     <interp inst="t18301028-147-person1268" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the morning these pots were stolen I had put one of them at the door of Mrs. Barclay, in Villiers-court, near to Mr. Pullen's; I saw three other pots there, and took particular notice of them - they seemed to be like these.</p>
               <p>Thomas delivered in a petition, soliciting for a lenient sentence.</p>
